&lt;p&gt;Come work with us to improve cancer services across west London&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join RM Partners West London Cancer Alliance as a Workforce Project Manager leading on the delivery of cancer workforce transformation projects. This key post will be support both South West London and North West London Integrated Care Systems (ICS’s) to develop cancer workforce plans, working closely with Health Education England (HEE), Macmillan and HR/Workforce colleagues at The Royal Marsden Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone with significant experience and understanding of the NHS and cancer workforce, underpinned with project management skills to deliver on specific workforce projects, and an ability to communicate and work across multiple stakeholders and funders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Michelle Chen, Senior R&amp;D Manager, michelle.chen@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
